"vote_average":0.166},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/ghUBVNrOEgWKvJiNvHLNupXd1EL.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/2pPrT2RjobK0Sqpk4Np4Ums6hMn.jpg","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/oLEJr1DdxZO4Zc3uZf7fWFAjsau.jpg","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/h9qfJtrqIMSMyHCnNe7gANBcDV9.jpg","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/nYfJ6SRjFqMYFoAxEGfe3NWFra8.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/n7ST7xGwx5ByoJa38qRvjaM88bV.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/8vVP4PUwP63xMiTMqan01qhZohi.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/oWfMD542qA2yRNTP2dGbhCTkFFm.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/5sQhdsN9I7GqjXJ6kZdpRomDE2L.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/tzUaW9EOb6YEvxrYued5a0GdOtV.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/5fhW1PCslXkNgj3aFdkndtOCVY2.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-02-25T03:58:02.225+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"","runtime":124,"tagline":"There are no partners in crime.","homepage":"","overview":"An aging thief hopes to retire and live off his ill-gotten wealth when a young kid convinces him into doing one last heist."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":124,"tagline":"Sie können den Coup nur gemeinsam landen. Doch die Beute will jeder für sich allein.","homepage":"","overview":"Der in die Jahre gekommene Meisterdieb Nick Wells lässt sich von seinem Auftraggeber Max zu einem letzten großen Coup überreden. Ziel ist ein französisches goldenes Königszepter im Wert von 30 Millionen Dollar. Allerdings muss Wells für diesen Auftrag zwei seiner wichtigsten Prinzipien über Bord werfen: Zum ersten Mal operiert er in seiner Heimatstadt Montreal und hat zudem noch einen Partner. Sein Partner Jack hat den komplizierten Coup schon akribisch vorbereitet: Als behinderter Reinigungsmann Brian getarnt hat er Zugang zum Zollgebäude, in dem das Zepter lagert. Mit seinem Insiderwissen sollte der Coup gelingen. Aber er braucht Nick, um den Tresor zu öffnen …"},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":124,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Nick Wells (De Niro), ladro professionista, decide di lasciare le attività illecite per dedicarsi ad una vita onesta. Presto però Max (Marlon Brando), suo buon amico e compagno negli affari, fa una proposta che Nick non può rifiutare: rubare uno scettro francese di inestimabile valore. Per questa missione gli viene affiancato Jackie Teller (Edward Norton), giovane ladro talentuoso e aggressivo."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"Komplo","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Nick Wells'in iki yaşamı vardır, bir yandan Montreal'da NYC isimli caz kulübünü işletirken diğer yandan profesyonel bir hırsızdır. Fakat artık hayatını riske atmaktansa, sevgilisiyle evlenip sadece kulübüne yoğunlaşmak istemektedir. Kısa süre sonra eski dostu ve yasadışı işlerindeki finans ortağı Max, Nick'in reddedemeyeceği bir teklifle çıkagelir: Tarihi ve paha biçilmez bir Fransız asası ülkeye yasadışı yollardan sokulurken ele geçirilmiştir ve Fransa'ya iade edilene dek Montreal gümrük deposunda son derece sıkı güvenlik önlemleriyle korunmaktadır.\r Şimdi Nick, Max'ın içerdeki adamı olan genç, yetenekli ve agresif hırsız Jackie Teller ile iş birliği yaparak eşsiz parçayı ele geçirmek ve tüm finansal problemlerinden bir anda kurtulmak istemektedir. Geriye tek bir soru kalır: Birbirlerine nasıl güvenecekler?"},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":124,"tagline":"Il n'y a pas de partenaires dans le crime.","homepage":"","overview":"Propriétaire d'un club de jazz à Montréal, Nick Wells prévoit de prendre sa retraite. En vingt ans passés au service du crime, aucun coffre n'a résisté à ce génie de la cambriole qui s'enorgueillit de ne travailler qu'en solo. Ce dernier décide néanmoins de monter un dernier coup, qui sera le couronnement de sa carrière. Max Baron, receleur et ami de longue date de Nick, lui propose de voler un sceptre d'or massif du XVIème siècle, entreposé dans les sous-sols de la Douane de Montréal. A priori, le coup est irréalisable. C'est pourquoi Max a confié au jeune Jackie Teller la lourde tâche d'aider Nick à accomplir ce vol. Mais en s'associant avec ce malfrat erratique qui n'aurait aucun scrupule à le doubler, Nick se retrouve plongé dans un engrenage infernal dont il aura beaucoup de mal à s'extirper."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"A szajré","runtime":123,"tagline":"Nincsenek bűntársak","homepage":"","overview":"A sötét szobában csak egy zseblámpa világítja meg a széfet. A fúró tompa zaját elnyomja a lentről felszüremlő ütemes dübörgés. Fémforgácsok hullnak a padlóra, feltárul a páncélszekrény ajtaja... Nck Wells eltökélte: visszavonul, ez volt az utolsó szajré. Összeköltözik barátnőjével, Diane-nel, és törvényes üzletére, a montreáli jazzklubra koncentrál. Azonban Maxnek, aki Nick barátja, üzlettársa és orgazdája, más tervei vannak. Rábeszéli a szakma legnagyobb profiját, hogy szegje meg a két legfontosabb szabályt - \"mindig egyedül dolgozz, és soha ne dolgozz abban a városban, ahol élsz,\" - és összehozza őt Jack Tellerrel. A fiatal, rámenős és tehetséges tolvajnak Nick kasszafúró tudományára van szüksége, hogy megcsinálja élete első nagy szajréját: egy milliókat érő műkincset, melyet a Montreáli Vámház falai mögött őriznek..."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"Медвежатник","runtime":0,"tagline":"«В преступлении не бывает партнеров»","homepage":"","overview":"Максу удается уговорить Ника Уэллса поступиться своими двумя самыми важными правилами: всегда работать в одиночку и никогда не грабить в своем городе. Макс нашел ему партнера. События начинают стремительно развиваться. Каждый из медвежатников старается обыграть другого. Планируемое ограбление держит всех в напряжении от начала и до конца. Развязка наступает неожиданно…"},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"The Score (Un golpe maestro)","runtime":124,"tagline":"No hay socios en el crimen.","homepage":"","overview":"Nick Wells (Robert De Niro), un famoso ladrón de guante blanco, ha decidido dejar para siempre su vida criminal y dedicarse a lo que realmente le interesa: su club de Jazz y su novia Diane (Angela Bassett). Pero Max (Marlon Brando) -su amigo, cómplice y socio- tiene otros planes para él: realizar su último golpe, un golpe maestro... Entrar en el edificio de Aduanas de Montreal y robar una obra de arte valorada en varios millones de dólares. Para ejecutar el plan necesitan la ayuda de Jackie Teller (Edward Norton), un joven y agresivo ladrón de mucho talento, experto en sistemas de alarma."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"The Score - Sem Saída","runtime":124,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Nick Wells é ladrão profissional e decide retirar-se, depois de quase ser apanhado no último assalto. É então que lhe fazem uma proposta irrecusável... Para um roubo perfeito, mas praticamente impossível, Nick é obrigado a unir-se a um jovem ladrão."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Rozgrywka","runtime":124,"tagline":"W tej grze nie ma wspólników.","homepage":"","overview":"Doświadczony kasiarz Nick Wells (Robert De Niro) postanawia ustatkować się i wraz ze swoją dziewczyną Diane (Angela Bassett) zająć się prowadzeniem legalnego klubu jazzowego w Montrealu. Jego przyjaciel i partner Max (Marlon Brando) ma jednak inne plany. Mocno zadłużony u mafijnego bossa postanawia nakłonić Nicka do jeszcze jednego ostatniego skoku: wraz z nowicjuszem Jackiem Tellerem (Edward Norton) mają wykraść z magazynu celnego berło warte 30 mln dolarów. Skuszony 6-milionową dniówką, Nick przystaje na propozycję. Spokojna robótka zmienia się jednak w wielce ryzykowną, grożącą wpadką akcję - zwłaszcza, gdy górę bierze nieokiełznana chciwość partnerów...\r Rozgrywka to jeden z najinteligentniejszych kryminałów, jaki kiedykolwiek nakręcono - z wieloma zaskakującymi zwrotami akcji.  [opis dystrybutora dvd]"},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"大买卖","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"偷窃老手尼克（罗伯特·德尼罗 Robert De Niro 饰）顺利完成了委托人的任务返回住所，但是在交接时委托人麦斯（马龙·白兰度 Marlon Brando饰）给他带来了一好一坏两个消息：坏消息是买主死掉了，尼克无法出货；好消息则是有一单四百万的大生意在等着他——需要尼可从海关大楼的地下室偷出国王的加冕权杖。预备和女友结婚的尼可不想再涉足偷窃，但是麦斯的合作者——乔装弱智打入海关内部的青年杰克（爱德华·诺顿 Edward Norton 饰）对这单生意锲而不舍，杰克终于打动尼可，与之结成了偷窃权杖的二人组合。杰克凭借出色的急智完成了准备工作，尼可对这位锋芒毕露的年青人要求严格，但又不乏暗暗的赞许。行动当夜，两人潜入海关，但事情的发展却出人意表…… ©豆瓣"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":124,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Nick Wells, een professionele crimineel, besluit het criminele leventje achter zich te laten. Zijn goede vriend Max komt met een plan dat Nick niet kan afslaan: een historisch Frans object is ontdekt terwijl het het land werd ingesmokkeld."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":124,"tagline":"Δεν υπάρχουν συνέταιροι στο έγκλημα.","homepage":"","overview":"Τώρα πια, η μοναδική έννοια του Νικ Γουέλς, πρώην επαγγελματία κλέφτη, είναι να ζήσει ήρεμα με την κοπέλα του Νταϊάν φροντίζοντας το NYC, το τζαζ κλαμπ που άνοιξε στο Μόντρεαλ. Παρόλα αυτά, ένας παλιός «συνάδελφος» δεν αργεί να τον προσεγγίσει και να παρασύρει τον Νικ για μια ακόμη φορά στη δράση με μια αληθινή πρόκληση: ένα ανεκτίμητο γαλλικό σκήπτρο, που κάποιοι προσπάθησαν ανεπιτυχώς να εισάγουν λαθραία στον Καναδά, φυλάσσεται στο τελωνείο του Μόντρεαλ, κάτω από δρακόντεια μέτρα ασφαλείας, με προορισμό τη Γαλλία. Ο Νικ διαθέτει λίγο χρόνο στη διάθεσή του για να συνεργαστεί με τον Τζάκι Κέλι, ένα νεαρό, χαρισματικό, αλλά ευέξαπτο και αλαζόνα επαγγελματία κλέφτη. Το πιο επικίνδυνο στην υπόθεση θα προκύψει όταν ο Νικ θα παραβιάσει τον κανόνα που πάντα ακολουθούσε: \"Να δουλεύεις πάντα μόνος\". Και οι τρεις συνεργοί θέλουν τα λάφυρα για τον εαυτό τους, αλλά για να ξεφύγουν και να επιβιώσουν χρειάζονται ο ένας τον άλλο."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Den dygtige internationale forbryder Nick Wells er parat til at trække sig tilbage med sin kæreste Diane og koncentrere sig om sin jazz klub. Han partner Max har dog andre planer og overtaler Nick til at bryde to af sine principper – han arbejder altid alene, og aldrig i samme by som han bor i. Nick skal arbejde samme med den unge talentfulde tyv Jackie om et kup mod toldbygningen i Montreal. Alle tre mænd bliver hurtigt besat om tanken af det store kup og vil gennemføre det for enhver pris."},"name":"Dansk","iso_639_1":"da","iso_3166_1":"DK","english_name":"Danish"},{"data":{"title":"الهدف","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"فيلم \"الهدف\" من بطولة دي نيرو و ادوارد نورتون، يحكي عن لص كبير في السن يفكر في التقاعد والعيش بعيدا مع ثروته الغير مشروعة  بشرط القيام بعملية سطو أخيرة، فهل ينجح؟"},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"SA","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"הפריצה","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"דרמת מתח. רוברט דה נירו מגלם גנב עתיר מוניטין, הרוצה לפרוש מעולם הפשע ולהתמסר לחברתו (אנג'לה באסט, \"קונטקט\", \"לנגן מהלב\") ולמועדון הג'אז שלו. אבל חברו ושותפו לעסקים (מרלון ברנדו) זקוק קשות למזומנים ומבקש ממנו לסייע בגניבת שרביט צרפתי קדום ויקר ערך מכספת של בית המכס במונטריאול, ולרגל המשימה הוא מצמיד לו גנב צעיר ושאפתן ,אדוארד נורטון,\"מועדון קרב\""},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"Kdo s koho","runtime":119,"tagline":"Zločin nezná bratra","homepage":"","overview":"Profesionální zloděj Nick Wells je rozhodnut skončit s dosavadním způsobem obživy. Má už dost a je ve věku, kdy se chce usadit, žít v klidu se svojí přítelkyní Dianou a věnovat se svému koníčku – jazzovému klubu, který v Montrealu vlastní. Ale překupník Max, jeho přítel a finanční partner, dostal tip na krádež století. Nabídka je tak lákavá, že Nick je posléze ochoten vzdát se i obou zásad, jimiž se vždycky ve své nelegální profesi řídil."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"A Cartada Final","runtime":124,"tagline":"Não há parceiros no crime","homepage":"","overview":"O ladrão profissional Nick Wells está prestes a executar um roubo quase impossível, mas, para isso, precisa unir forças com um jovem cúmplice. A aliança duvidosa, formada por um amigo, atrapalha os planos de Nick, que pretendia se aposentar da vida criminosa e ficar com sua noiva, Diane. Agora, ele terá que infringir sua regra mais importante, que é a de trabalhar sempre sozinho."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Ведмежатник","runtime":0,"tagline":"Партнерів у злочині немає.","homepage":"","overview":"Максу вдається умовити Ніка Велса поступитися своїми двома найважливішими правилами: завжди працювати поодинці і ніколи не грабувати у своєму місті. Макс знайшов йому партнера. Події починають стрімко розвиватися. Кожен із злочинців намагається обіграти іншого. Плановане пограбування тримає всіх в напрузі від початку і до кінця. Розв'язка настає несподівано..."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"鬼計神偷","runtime":120,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"尼克魏斯準備洗手不幹，他打算和他女友黛安退隱江湖，安安份份地在蒙特婁經營一家爵士餐廳，但是他的掮客、好友及生意夥伴麥斯卻另有打算。  麥斯計畫幹下最後一票，也是最大的一票，他用盡方法說服尼克接下這個不可能的任務，也違反了他身為神偷以來一直奉行的兩個原則，那就是絕不和人搭檔，絕不在居住的城市犯案，但是這次麥斯卻幫他找到一個年輕氣盛卻聰明絕頂的新秀神偷傑克泰勒當搭檔，年少輕狂的傑克正在磨拳擦掌，準備幹下這天大的一票，也就是被深鎖在防守嚴密的蒙特婁海關大廈裡的一個無價之寶。  自大輕浮的菜鳥準備大幹一場，而謹慎穩重的老鳥只想急流勇退，加上年老力衰的掮客也面臨重大危機，於是這樣的組合一定產生火爆的衝突，不只是鬥智也鬥力，最後的贏家到底會是誰？"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Прецакването","runtime":119,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Партньор на Ник ще бъде нахаканият младок Джак Телър (Едуард Нортън). Великолепно надиграване на трима от най-изтъкнатите за своите поколения артисти, всеки от които е доказал класата си като възпитаник на прочутия актьорски “метод на Станиславски”. Брандо може и да е огромен и да се движи трудно, но уменията му са си свежи както винаги. Франк Оз не е типичният режисьор на трилъри, но с такива чудесни актьори се е справил повече от добре; съществен принос за повишаване на напрежението има музиката на Хауърд Шор. Божествената Анджела Басет играе Даян – приятелката на Ник Уелс."},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"Scor final","runtime":124,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Nick, un spărgător de seifuri gata de pensionare, Max, un tip bombastic, și Jackie, un hoț talentat și iute la mânie, fac echipă pentru a jefui Casa Vămii din Montreal."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"Cuenta final","runtime":124,"tagline":"No hay socios en el crimen.","homepage":"","overview":"Nick Wells (de Niro), un ladrón profesional, proyecta un robo tan complejo que se ve obligado a buscar la ayuda de un hábil cómplice (Norton), vulnerando así la regla de oro de su trabajo: actuar siempre solo. Además, este golpe echaría por tierra los planes de Nick de abandonar el mundo del crimen para irse a vivir con su novia."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Plen","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Srpski","iso_639_1":"sr","iso_3166_1":"RS","english_name":"Serbian"},{"data":{"title":"Obračun","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ostareli poklicni tat bi se rad upokojil in živel od nakradenega bogastva, a ga prijatelj in sodelavec prepriča v še zadnji tatinski podvig. Gotova priložnost se nazadnje sprevrže v tvegano igro življenja in smrti."},"name":"Slovenščina","iso_639_1":"sl","iso_3166_1":"SI","english_name":"Slovenian"},{"data":{"title":"Kto z koho","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Slovenčina","iso_639_1":"sk","iso_3166_1":"SK","english_name":"Slovak"},{"data":{"title":"Atlygis","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Nikas Velsas užsidirbdavo pragyvenimui atlikdamas nešvarius darbelius. Tai buvo įvairios aferos, neįtikėtinos apgaulės ir kruopščiai suplanuotos vagystės. Vieną gražią dieną vyrukas nusprendžia atsikratyti savo kriminalinės praeities ir džiaugtis ramiu gyvenimu kartu su mylima stiuardese Diana. Jis įgyvendina didžiausią savo svajonę – įkuria jaukų džiazo klubą Monrealyje. Tačiau šis sumanymas nepatinka senam Niko pažįstamam ir geram draugui."},"name":"Lietuvių","iso_639_1":"lt","iso_3166_1":"LT","english_name":"Lithuanian"},{"data":{"title":"Tko je kome smjestio","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ostarjeli lopov nada se da će se povući i živjeti od svog nelegalno stečenog bogatstva kada ga mladi klinac uvjeri da izvrši još jednu pljačku."},"name":"Hrvatski","iso_639_1":"hr","iso_3166_1":"HR","english_name":"Croatian"},{"data":{"title":"Le grand coup","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"CA","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Skoor - kavalam jääb peale","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Eesti","iso_639_1":"et","iso_3166_1":"EE","english_name":"Estonian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Huippuvaras Nick Wells on pӓӓttӓnyt jӓttӓӓ murtohommat, asettua aloilleen Montrealiin tyttӧystӓvӓnsӓ Dianen kanssa ja keskittyӓ lailliseen bisnekseensӓ jazzklubin omistajana. Nickin ystӓvӓllӓ ja kumppanilla Maxilla on kuitenkin muita suunnitelmia. Max on suurissa veloissa ja pyytӓӓ Nickiӓ hoitamaan vielӓ yhden keikan: varastamaan tullikamarilta 30 milijoonan dollarin arvoisen valtikan apurinaan nuori varas Jack Teller. Kuuden miljoonan dollarin palkkion houkettelemana Nick vastentahtoisesti suostuu Maxin ehdotukseen. Alun perin helppo ryӧstӧ osoittautuu kuitenkin luultua monimutkaisemmaksi..."},"name":"suomi","iso_639_1":"fi","iso_3166_1":"FI","english_name":"Finnish"},{"data":{"title":"스코어","runtime":0,"tagline":"최고는 결코 둘이 될 수 없다","homepage":"","overview":"전설적인 금고털이범 닉 웰즈는 이제 은퇴 후 자신의 여자친구 다이앤과 재즈 클럽을 운영하면서 평범하고 합법적인 생활을 하며 몬트리올에 정착하려 한다. 어느 날 오랜 친구이자 파트너로서 일해온 장물아비 맥스에게 재정적인 문제가 생기게 되고, 이에 닉에게 마지막으로 한탕 크게 할 것을 제안하게 된다. 맥스는 이번 계획을 위해 젊고, 공격적인 유능한 도둑인 잭 펠러를 끌어들이게 되고 최고의 금고 털이 기술을 가지고 있는 닉을 설득하여 잭과 함께 대박을 터트리려 한다. 각자의 이익과 한 목표를 위해 모인 그들이지만 또 다른 각자의 꿍꿍이를 숨긴 채 전대미문의 몬트리올 세관 금고 털이 계획이 진행되는데..."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Mästertjuven Nick Wells är hjärnan bakom en nästan omöjlig kupp, som kräver att han slår sig samman med en ung och slug medbrottsling. Den osannolika alliansen, iscensatt av Nicks trogna kumpan Max, sätter stopp för Nicks planer att bli hederlig och leva ett lugnt familjeliv med sin fästmö Diane. Men vad som framstår som ännu värre än att bryta ett löfte till sin fästmö är att Nick måste bryta sin viktigaste regel: Arbeta alltid ensam..."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"スコア","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"デ・ニーロとノートンの新旧カメレオン俳優が激突! 完全防備されたフランス王家の秘宝を狙って、犯罪のプロがタッグを組む。最後の最後まで気が抜けないスリリングなクライム・ムービー。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"ผ่ารหัสปล้นเหนือเมฆ","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"นักเปิดเซฟที่พร้อมจะลาออกอย่างนิก นักขายของโจรสุดหรู แม็กซ์ และโจรที่เอาแน่เอานอนไม่ได้อย่างแจ็กกี้ รวมตัวกันเพื่อปล้นโรงศุลกากรของมอนทรีอัล"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"ანგარიში","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"ხანში შესული პროფესიონალი ქურდი თავს ანებებს კრიმინალურ ცხოვრებას და დარჩენილი წლების მშვიდად გატარებას გეგმავს, მაგრამ ახალგაზრდა მეგობარი უკანასკნელ საქმეზე წასასვლელად დაიყოლიებს."},"name":"ქართული","iso_639_1":"ka","iso_3166_1":"GE","english_name":"Georgian"},{"data":{"title":"Un colp mestre","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Nick Wells (Robert De Niro), un famós lladre de guant blanc, ha decidit deixar per sempre la vida criminal i dedicar-se al que realment li interessa: el seu club de Jazz i la seva núvia Diane (Angela Bassett). Però Max (Marlon Brando) -el seu amic, còmplice i soci- té altres plans per a ell: fer el seu darrer cop, un cop mestre... Entrar a l'edifici de Duanes de Montreal i robar una obra d'art valorada en diversos milions de dòlars. Per executar el pla necessiten l'ajuda de Jackie Teller (Edward Norton), un lladre jove i agressiu de molt talent, expert en sistemes d'alarma."},"name":"Català","iso_639_1":"ca","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Catalan"},{"data":{"title":"Siêu Trộm","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Một tên trộm lớn tuổi hy vọng có thể nghỉ hưu và sống bằng số tiền bất chính của mình khi một đứa trẻ thuyết phục hắn thực hiện một vụ trộm cuối cùng."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"鬼計神偷","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"尼克魏斯準備洗手不幹，他打算和他女友黛安退隱江湖，安安份份地在蒙特婁經營一家爵士餐廳，但是他的掮客、好友及生意夥伴麥斯卻另有打算。\r 麥斯計畫幹下最後一票，也是最大的一票，他用盡方法説服尼克接下這個不可能的任務，也違反了他身為神偷以來一直奉行的兩個原則，那就是絕不和人搭檔，絕不在居住的城市犯案，但是這次麥斯卻幫他找到一個年輕氣盛卻聰明絕頂的新秀神偷傑克泰勒當搭檔，年少輕狂的傑克正在磨拳擦掌，準備幹下這天大的一票，也就是被深鎖在防守嚴密的蒙特婁海關大廈裏的一個無價之寶。\r 自大輕浮的菜鳥準備大幹一場，而謹慎穩重的老鳥只想急流勇退，加上年老力衰的掮客也面臨重大危機，於是這樣的組合一定產生火爆的衝突，不只是鬥智也鬥力，最後的贏家到底會是誰？"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"61f85ff5cb802800921bc243","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/61f85ff5cb802800921bc243","author":"JPV852","content":"A go-to for a solid heist-thriller that features two great performances by De Niro and Norton with honorable mention to Brando who looked a little worse for wear. Not the top notch in the genre but still a breezy but still suspense-filled watch if you don't want anything thought-provoking. Still makes me chuckle that it was Frank Oz to be the one to direct three generations of great actors... **3.75/5**","created_at":"2022-01-31T22:17:25.792Z","updated_at":"2022-01-31T22:17:25.792Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":8,"username":"JPV852","avatar_path":"/xNLOqXXVJf9m7WngUMLIMFsjKgh.jpg"}}],"recommendations":[{"id":4967,"adult":false,"title":"Keeping the Faith","video":false,"overview":"Best friends since they were kids, Rabbi Jacob Schram and Father Brian Finn are dynamic and popular young men living and working on New York's Upper West Side. When Anna Reilly, once their childhood friend and now grown into a beautiful corporate executive, suddenly returns to the city, she reenters Jake and Brian's lives and hearts with a vengeance. Sparks fly and an unusual and complicated love triangle ensues.","genre_ids":[35,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8847,"vote_count":652,"poster_path":"/9NF199FTvHr9ggqdBTVbPhF1MGk.jpg","release_date":"2000-04-14","vote_average":6.1,"backdrop_path":"/3xJFFU3YF9WcpK2WXDF15zVcSQZ.jpg","original_title":"Keeping the Faith","original_language":"en"},{"id":9932,"adult":false,"title":"Analyze That","video":false,"overview":"The mafia's Paul Vitti is back in prison and will need some serious counseling when he gets out. Naturally, he returns to his analyst Dr. Ben Sobel for help and finds that Sobel needs some serious help himself as he has inherited the family practice, as well as an excess stock of stress.","genre_ids":[35,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.8165,"vote_count":1351,"poster_path":"/q3R6Hno3WFfIkHQg7CeVAEOcHQQ.jpg","release_date":"2002-12-06","vote_average":5.826,"backdrop_path":"/squEMJDrsY7ooVNFqbTSdIVO4Qh.jpg","original_title":"Analyze That","original_language":"en"},{"id":395449,"adult":false,"title":"The New Life of Paul Sneijder","video":false,"overview":"Following a rare accident, Paul Sneijder opened his eyes to the reality of his life as a \"senior manager\" in Montreal: his work no longer interested him, his wife annoyed him and deceived him, his two sons despised him ... How can we continue to live under these conditions? Starting with a change of profession: dog walker for example! Will his relatives accept this change that will turn him into a free man?","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.2944,"vote_count":58,"poster_path":"/55KErHWVB6Vnx31wJx0EUSSaT0p.jpg","release_date":"2016-06-08","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/5WLAICo18QSe7mNCNIEGwMIfO7z.jpg","original_title":"La Nouvelle Vie de Paul Sneijder","original_language":"fr"},{"id":26326,"adult":false,"title":"Rock 'n' Roll High School","video":false,"overview":"A group of rock-music-loving students, with the help of the Ramones, take over their school to combat its newly installed oppressive administration.","genre_ids":[35,10402],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6766,"vote_count":153,"poster_path":"/kxoDBrtLqMsjMlfWb2caRRY92Xg.jpg","release_date":"1979-04-20","vote_average":6.3,"backdrop_path":"/5LIIvrECXVaWyiwWrflkOJh9og0.jpg","original_title":"Rock 'n' Roll High School","original_language":"en"},{"id":47426,"adult":false,"title":"South of the Border","video":false,"overview":"A road trip across five countries to explore the social and political movements as well as the mainstream media's misperception of South America while interviewing seven of its elected presidents.","genre_ids":[99],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3948,"vote_count":41,"poster_path":"/8JwbicUe7NsPk6azviHzUGpXT41.jpg","release_date":"2009-09-07","vote_average":5.9,"backdrop_path":"/xsIUIFmc7lVmuzOHSm4TKHqpiFb.jpg","original_title":"South of the Border","original_language":"en"},{"id":5353,"adult":false,"title":"The Hunting Party","video":false,"overview":"A young journalist, an experienced cameraman and a discredited reporter find their bold plan to capture Bosnia's top war criminal quickly spiraling out of control when a UN representative mistakes them for a CIA hit squad.","genre_ids":[28,12,53,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.993,"vote_count":348,"poster_path":"/kXUfQGa7BoW856hDYAFtZLtiAAQ.jpg","release_date":"2007-09-03","vote_average":6.497,"backdrop_path":"/k1dXZF6vyVgtmppyXWLZd9FmqmY.jpg","original_title":"The Hunting Party","original_language":"en"},{"id":335970,"adult":false,"title":"Joe Dirt 2: Beautiful Loser","video":false,"overview":"When happy family man Joe Dirt finds himself transported to the recent past, he begins an epic journey to get back to his loved ones in the present.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5443,"vote_count":164,"poster_path":"/nde744Wjaj11BXA4npXcByLDMkw.jpg","release_date":"2015-07-16","vote_average":4.93,"backdrop_path":"/8xpVDoRy0fZzhMSUBG8nksctu9i.jpg","original_title":"Joe Dirt 2: Beautiful Loser","original_language":"en"},{"id":48213,"adult":false,"title":"The Ogre","video":false,"overview":"Frenchman Abel Tiffauges is a naive man who lives a simple life working as a mechanic. Falsely accused of being a child abuser, he is recruited as a soldier when World War II begins, but is captured soon and taken to the heart of Nazi Germany.","genre_ids":[18,10752],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4821,"vote_count":46,"poster_path":"/ybLzxBiB9qiiqyANLj8RGs2Dkp3.jpg","release_date":"1996-09-12","vote_average":6.3,"backdrop_path":"/rIfaCpgE59tkjZbAOIZnuXvhCBv.jpg","original_title":"Der Unhold","original_language":"de"},{"id":637805,"adult":false,"title":"Vikruthi","video":false,"overview":"Mistaking the sleeping passenger on his train for a drunk, a young man posts a picture of him online, unaware of his impulsive act's ugly repercussions.","genre_ids":[35,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.9038,"vote_count":12,"poster_path":"/lhyf1hRUXib411aUWtEARVvZb3z.jpg","release_date":"2019-10-04","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/k2TBrH1rDY96NyxLds4vWBtfuOq.jpg","original_title":"വികൃതി","original_language":"ml"},{"id":415036,"adult":false,"title":"Open at Night","video":false,"overview":"One night to change everything. One night to save a theater, one night to change one's perspective about life. Luigi will push and pull Faeza with him everywhere around Paris an entire night to save his theater.","genre_ids":[18,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8679,"vote_count":72,"poster_path":"/fEH20nWuzDJqS34OU9mf1ZjO2rV.jpg","release_date":"2017-01-11","vote_average":6.1,"backdrop_path":"/pit1R4qFSDg98mVGjHJONIFScd2.jpg","original_title":"Ouvert la nuit","original_language":"fr"},{"id":62496,"adult":false,"title":"La fame e la sete","video":false,"overview":"Alex, Ivo and Pacifico three Sicilian twin brothers are reunited for their father's funeral.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.2591,"vote_count":65,"poster_path":"/xsZq9Nk9HihgJE3HnWScQacfhO.jpg","release_date":"1999-03-19","vote_average":6.431,"backdrop_path":"/t0n0Anv1mdorX0jWftEkBDa6pzQ.jpg","original_title":"La fame e la sete","original_language":"it"},{"id":19419,"adult":false,"title":"Screwed","video":false,"overview":"A chauffeur kidnaps his rich boss's dog to hold it for ransom, but when she accidentally gets the dog back, she thinks that it's the chauffeur who's been kidnapped.","genre_ids":[28,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.4778,"vote_count":106,"poster_path":"/m6FfMbH1ga1Kp5QI9Nm0ETOIG64.jpg","release_date":"2000-05-12","vote_average":5.5,"backdrop_path":"/6o8y8fNo6eIgmS2jRux150LQwwj.jpg","original_title":"Screwed","original_language":"en"},{"id":304613,"adult":false,"title":"Charlie's Farm","video":false,"overview":"Four friends head into the Australian Outback to investigate an urban legend about Charlie's Farm, where legend has it that an angry mob killed a sadistic family, and encounter a demented giant with a big thirst for revenge.","genre_ids":[27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7598,"vote_count":112,"poster_path":"/kTYBbY9AvbpNdcKEBcK5OwEu72H.jpg","release_date":"2014-12-04","vote_average":4.7,"backdrop_path":"/7ipuL3OMEMpRlizxnbgX0jVNmol.jpg","original_title":"Charlie's Farm","original_language":"en"},{"id":75011,"adult":false,"title":"How I Unleashed World War II, Part I: The Escape","video":false,"overview":"On the night of August 31, 1939, Dolas, from a platoon reinforcing a train station on the German border, falls asleep in a train car and unknowingly crosses into Germany. The moment he shoots a German, who he thinks is a saboteur, the German invasion of Poland begins, and Dolas is convinced it was his fault. He is taken to Stalag POW camp, the first destination in his odyssey around Europe.","genre_ids":[35,10752,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4406,"vote_count":60,"poster_path":"/2smM51Pz6Bt2jjabd7UPyVkM4wu.jpg","release_date":"1970-04-02","vote_average":7.6,"backdrop_path":"/gujTminHou8yfdVhJxn4wiGuTpR.jpg","original_title":"Jak rozpętałem drugą wojnę światową: Cz. 1 - Ucieczka","original_language":"pl"},{"id":44113,"adult":false,"title":"Stone","video":false,"overview":"Parole officer Jack Mabry has only a few weeks left before retirement and wishes to finish out the cases he's been assigned. One such case is that of Gerald 'Stone' Creeson, a convicted arsonist who is up for parole. Jack is initially reluctant to indulge Stone in the coarse banter he wishes to pursue and feels little sympathy for the prisoner's pleads for an early release. Seeing little hope in convincing Jack himself, Stone arranges for his wife to seduce the officer, but motives and intentions steadily blur amidst the passions and buried secrets of the corrupted players in this deadly game of deception.","genre_ids":[18,53,28,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.668,"vote_count":721,"poster_path":"/mcdN6DntOAOtKNQKcRKnfFayFis.jpg","release_date":"2010-10-07","vote_average":5.294,"backdrop_path":"/vJFZLY3v9Ol8BGzVLNTZy2z3jvK.jpg","original_title":"Stone","original_language":"en"},{"id":28509,"adult":false,"title":"Komodo vs. Cobra","video":false,"overview":"A team of environmentalists, including a reporter, her camera man, and an environmentalist's famous girlfriend charter a boat and with the captain, sail to a military island. They suspect the island is hosting to illegal activities. Upon arrival, however, they find no one. They finally reach a deserted house, where they find Dr. Susan Richardson, who tells them that everyone on the island is dead, including her father. Richardson's team were working on a compound that could make edible plants grow to super size, however the military intervened with plans of their own. They wanted to test the compound's effects on animals, and proceeded to feed it to several komodo dragons and cobras.","genre_ids":[27,878,10770],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6482,"vote_count":68,"poster_path":"/2dLwpe18MC3nIF5MmkWuB8waba9.jpg","release_date":"2005-08-19","vote_average":4,"backdrop_path":"/a8ROQ0ATsV0y92D0kplsIqdXxCQ.jpg","original_title":"Komodo vs. Cobra","original_language":"en"},{"id":142645,"adult":false,"title":"The Making of 'Cape Fear'","video":false,"overview":"A retrospective documentary on the making of Cape Fear (1991) and Cape Fear (1962).","genre_ids":[99],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5008,"vote_count":18,"poster_path":"/zjtHl0hf737Cbpsz11l4wHEjziU.jpg","release_date":"2001-09-18","vote_average":7.278,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"The Making of 'Cape Fear'","original_language":"en"},{"id":97351,"adult":false,"title":"Phir Bhi Dil Hai Hindustani","video":false,"overview":"Two rival reporters team up to help prove the innocence of a man set to be hanged for the murder of a politician.","genre_ids":[10749,35,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.9209,"vote_count":88,"poster_path":"/7VvNZVMbUcxwfdLZlUSZnKFYu0p.jpg","release_date":"2000-01-21","vote_average":6.6,"backdrop_path":"/dUBHrBI9nC3PNYkKLF5NOE3aiuh.jpg","original_title":"फिर भी दिल है हिंदुस्तानी","original_language":"hi"},{"id":11095,"adult":false,"title":"I Often Think of Piroschka","video":false,"overview":"Andreas, a young German student comes to Hungary on an exchange programme. In the Hungarian village he falls in love with the stationmaster's daughter Piroschka and spends much of his time with her. They have an enchanting summer until Andreas gets an invitation to join another young woman at a nearby resort. Piroschka is jealous and follows him there, causing trouble. It takes a long time for Andreas and Piroschka to even talk to each other again. When Andreas has to leave Hungary at the end of his holiday, he is determined to return some day.","genre_ids":[10749,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3336,"vote_count":25,"poster_path":"/obmyNjPpBNk8T3vwpAJxHW2EMFW.jpg","release_date":"1955-12-29","vote_average":6.9,"backdrop_path":"/qr2bvaG5wNlCzw61GBJzBF8eC1t.jpg","original_title":"Ich denke oft an Piroschka","original_language":"de"},{"id":9546,"adult":false,"title":"Ricochet","video":false,"overview":"An attorney is terrorized by the criminal he put away years ago when he was a cop.","genre_ids":[80,53,28,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.3072,"vote_count":353,"poster_path":"/5isHYEcUY0nE90uMhkGrs1nnal.jpg","release_date":"1991-10-04","vote_average":6.1,"backdrop_path":"/u4pJrlxr4lEEmwVAaU5KrEV1hLp.jpg","original_title":"Ricochet","original_language":"en"}],"similar_content":[{"id":463005,"adult":false,"title":"Moreno","video":false,"overview":"When Chris arrives at the village of T'boli in lake Sebu, South Cotabato, he thought he has left his dark recent past behind. He is working on commission as a video documentarist to make a profile on the women T'boli and their changing views on multiple marriages. The most affluent men, called Datu, marry more than once and each time pays dowry to the family of the women they marry. When a young T'boli woman, Ngapon, tells Chris that she wants to be free from a marriage that was set by her parents and to go to Manila, Chris begins to confront waht he left in the city. Like the proud Datu with many wives, Chris has Denver, a bronze skinned lover in Manila, who is proud of his relationships. Denver lives with Chris in an apartment as partners yet he still goes into sexual and emotional relationships with other men. Ngapon's quest for freedom becomes Chris journey to a very sad dark past.  - Written by Anonymous","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.245,"vote_count":8,"poster_path":"/oKRDC0ul0qXzaLBeis8k2aHSKTl.jpg","release_date":"2007-06-20","vote_average":4.1,"backdrop_path":"/tmULj2zOy644sKW4yayc1fqimYX.jpg","original_title":"Moreno","original_language":"tl"},{"id":26,"adult":false,"title":"Walk on Water","video":false,"overview":"Eyal, an Israeli Mossad agent, is given the mission to track down and kill the very old Alfred Himmelman, an ex-Nazi officer, who might still be alive. Pretending to be a tourist guide, he befriends his grandson Axel, in Israel to visit his sister Pia. The two men set out on a tour of the country, during which Axel challenges Eyal's values.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.7146,"vote_count":91,"poster_path":"/mVWFN3RaBFLuJRtRLPebatX9qPq.jpg","release_date":"2004-02-05","vote_average":6.835,"backdrop_path":"/z5YFbE9VVHwDXbXbqZdoO6THqPs.jpg","original_title":"ללכת על המים","original_language":"he"},{"id":271388,"adult":false,"title":"Velociraptor","video":false,"overview":"During the end of the world, two best friends walk around their city, talking about their sex lives, and one of them reveals they are still a virgin.","genre_ids":[35,18,14],"popularity":0.2151,"vote_count":19,"poster_path":"/mGuQBdevB7q2JK6PMqYjCVrXN8W.jpg","release_date":"2014-06-07","vote_average":5.132,"backdrop_path":"/6feb1sjJdNvXQJXw9n6G07SZIR3.jpg","original_title":"Velociraptor","original_language":"es"},{"id":1816,"adult":false,"title":"A Chorus Line","video":false,"overview":"A group of dancers congregate on the stage of a Broadway theatre to audition for a new musical production directed by Zach. After the initial eliminations, seventeen hopefuls remain, among them Cassie, who once had a tempestuous romantic relationship with Zach. She is desperate enough for work to humble herself and audition for him; whether he's willing to let professionalism overcome his personal feelings about their past remains to be seen.","genre_ids":[18,10402],"popularity":0.924,"vote_count":196,"poster_path":"/bQzbO6y6gxePrEcU57Su8HJ9UdH.jpg","release_date":"1985-12-10","vote_average":6.227,"backdrop_path":"/AvPLYsn8SyDWFFBzBqmsohZ5p8x.jpg","original_title":"A Chorus Line","original_language":"en"},{"id":1831,"adult":false,"title":"The Next Best Thing","video":false,"overview":"A comedy-drama about best friends - one a straight woman, Abbie, the other a gay man, Robert - who decide to have a child together. Five years later, Abbie falls in love with a straight man and wants to move away with her and Robert's little boy Sam, and a nasty custody battle ensues.","genre_ids":[35,18,10749],"popularity":0.6853,"vote_count":195,"poster_path":"/iYK1ZUtY4etcn91glUmrGuZRH6M.jpg","release_date":"2000-03-03","vote_average":5.3,"backdrop_path":"/gA319UUESvNt5jCsQ9YqSidJ2CE.jpg","original_title":"The Next Best Thing","original_language":"en"},{"id":1833,"adult":false,"title":"Rent","video":false,"overview":"In New York City's gritty East Village, a group of bohemians strive for success and acceptance while enduring the obstacles of poverty, illness and the AIDS epidemic.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":2.7238,"vote_count":589,"poster_path":"/fomBrfOHWxlaVcjPk4yCQgIwAnh.jpg","release_date":"2005-11-17","vote_average":6.845,"backdrop_path":"/Aby2bp5yZYLSvs8Ql32bZAamTFb.jpg","original_title":"Rent","original_language":"en"},{"id":465534,"adult":false,"title":"Washed Hands","video":false,"overview":"An efficiency expert is called in to downsize a trucking company and the employees fight to establish a union to save their jobs.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.1811,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/roiWIzxDxujaBNxBay7Psq335YM.jpg","release_date":"1958-01-01","vote_average":5.8,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Les mains nettes","original_language":"fr"},{"id":1808,"adult":false,"title":"Velvet Goldmine","video":false,"overview":"Almost a decade since larger-than-life glam-rock enigma Brian Slade disappeared from public eye, an investigative journalist is on assignment to uncover the truth behind his former idol.","genre_ids":[18,10402],"popularity":1.4349,"vote_count":534,"poster_path":"/bsuSac0PldPFcOtR1Vioe7VBF4l.jpg","release_date":"1998-08-28","vote_average":6.875,"backdrop_path":"/zUs2GW4rPSIsfzBp0GtXaQR2mqk.jpg","original_